GWA_NAME, A.IPWON_DATE IPWON_DATE, A.IPWON_RESER_YN IPWON_RESER_YN, A.IPWON_TYPE IPWON_TYPE, 'N' COUSULT_GUBUN, SUBSTR(FN_OCS_INP_ORDER_STATUS_CHECK(A.BUNHO, A.PKINP1001, :f_order_date, :f_input_gubun), 1, 1) JINRYO_END_YN, NULL CONSULT_KEY , FN_BAS_LOAD_COMMON_DOCTOR_YN(A.GWA, A.DOCTOR, :f_order_date) COMMONT_DOCTOR_YN, NULL TOIWON_DATE, 'Y' JAEWON_YN, PK_KEY, A.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG, FN_BAS_LOAD_HO_DONG_NAME(A.HO_DONG1, :f_order_date) HO_DONG_NAME, A.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE, FN_BAS_LOAD_HO_CODE_NAME(A.HO_DONG1, A.HO_CODE1, :f_order_date) HO_CODE_NAME, B.BUNHO BUNHO, B.SUNAME SUNAME, B.SUNAME2 SUNAME2, B.SEX SEX, LTRIM(TO_CHAR(TRUNC(MONTHS_BETWEEN(:f_order_date, B.BIRTH)/12 ), '999')) AGE, B.GUBUN GUBUN, FN_BAS_LOAD_GUBUN_NAME(B.GUBUN, :f_order_date) GUBUN_NAME, A.DOCTOR DOCTOR, FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, :f_order_date) DOCTOR_NAME, A.GWA GWA, FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, :f_order_date) GWA_NAME, A.IPWON_DATE IPWON_DATE, NULL IPWON_RESER_YN, A.IPWON_TYPE IPWON_TYPE, 'N' COUSULT_GUBUN, SUBSTR(FN_OCS_INP_ORDER_STATUS_CHECK(A.BUNHO, A.PKINP1001, :f_order_date, :f_input_gubun), 1, 1) JINRYO_END_YN, NULL CONSULT_KEY , FN_BAS_LOAD_COMMON_DOCTOR_YN(A.GWA, A.DOCTOR, :f_order_date) COMMONT_DOCTOR_YN, TO_CHAR(A.TOIWON_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') TOIWON_DATE, 'N' JAEWON_YN, 'N'||RPAD(NVL(A.HO_DONG1, '0'), 4, '0')||RPAD(A.HO_CODE1, 10)||A.BUNHO||LTRIM(TO_CHAR(A.PKINP1001, '0000000000')) CONT_KEY FROM (SELECT Z.* FROM INP1001 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE () AND Z.PKINP1001 = (SELECT MAX (A.PKINP1001) FROM INP1001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = Z.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = Z.BUNHO AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NOT NULL)) A ,OUT0101 B WHERE A.IPWON_DATE <= :f_order_date AND A.BUNHO LIKE :f_bunho AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(A.HO_DONG1,'EMPTY') LIKE TRIM(:f_ho_dong) AND NVL(A.HO_CODE1,'EMPTY') LIKE TRIM(:f_ho_code) AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO ) AA WHERE AA.JAEWON_YN = :f_jaewon_yn ORDER BY 5

data.value: SELECT BLD_GUBUN ,PKOCS2005 ,BUNHO ,FKINP1001 ,ORDER_DATE ,INPUT_GUBUN ,INPUT_ID ,PK_SEQ ,DIRECT_GUBUN ,DIRECT_CODE ,DIRECT_CODE_D ,DIRECT_CONT1 ,DIRECT_CONT1_D ,DIRECT_CONT2 ,DIRECT_CONT2_D ,DIRECT_CONT3 ,DIRECT_CONT3_D ,NOMIMONO ,KUMJISIK ,DRT_FROM_DATE ,DRT_TO_DATE ,CONTINUE_YN FROM OCS2005 WHERE (:f_jaewon_yn = 'Y' AND FKINP1001 = ( SELECT B.PKINP1001 FROM VW_OCS_INP1001_RES_01 B WHERE B.BUNHO = :f_bunho ) OR :f_jaewon_yn = 'N' AND FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001) AND DIRECT_GUBUN = '03' AND FKOCS6015 IS NULL AND BLD_GUBUN = :f_bld_gubun AND HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code ORDER BY DRT_FROM_DATE
